com.camerontec.util.concurrent.circularbuffer

Interface Movable<S,T,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The source type.
    T - The target type.
    R - The move result type.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientMouldUdp64Session

    public interface Movable<S,T,R>
    Interface indicating an object is movable to the specified target type.

    Typically this is used to transfer ownership of the internal state of an object to the target.
